author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This morning I was looking at how the Switch 2 apparently needs you to have an Internet connection to even use the device, I saw the outrage and feel somewhat vindicated when talking about this near a decade ago. This time I feel the outrage is a bit selective because we've slowly normalized this behaviour when we shouldn't have. Thanks for watching!

title: The Switch 2 Is Technically A Brick...

author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be Google and it's constant destruction of it's search engine. This was once an institution to browse the Internet in it's infancy and in the last few years it's been bloated and modified with so many features that it begins to fail in what it was initially designed for. Thanks for watching!

title: Google Has Completely Ruined Its Search Engine...
